content:

This is the website for the 2010 graphic design class shop, [make, do](http://makedoshop.com).

The typeface for Make, Do's logo is Vergi, by [Alpkan Kirayoglu](http://alpabets.com), the type for the rest of the site is Typotheque's Plan Grotesque goes through their web font service.

The whole site is backed by a json database and navigation happens via jquery-address, which permits deep-linking and nice animation effects. HTML/CSS/JS (2010)
